      "text": "IMO:  #HTML #CSS #JavaScript\n\nI love making little #PowerShell scripts that write other languages.\n\nBasically making webby stuff becomes:\n\n./index.html.ps1 > ./index.html\n\nOr, if you're feeling fancy:\n\n./index.html.ps1 | some-layout-function > ./index.html\n\nTrick is language agnostic though."
